         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne, 1st July 1891 ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ I have the honor to report that Mr. J. R. Tovey, who was appointed to the position of Third Herbarium Assistant on 10th December last on probation, ¶ See also J. Ma...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">91.07.01a<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Thomas Wilson</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">S91/6265, unit 612, VPRS 3992/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Office. Public Record Office, Victoria.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS written by G. Luehmann and signed by M.</p>
               </note>Melbourne, 1st July 1891</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to report that Mr. J. R. Tovey, who was appointed to the position of Third Herbarium Assistant on 10th December last on probation,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="background-color: #FFFF00; ">See also J. Mackenzie, Secretary, Public Service Board to J. Munro, Chief Secretary, 13 July 1891 (R91/6601, unit 612, VPRS 3992/P, PROV).</seg>
                     </p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; margin-left: 0in; text-indent: 0in; color: #C00000; "
                        xml:lang="en">We don't have this letter transcribed. Is note necessary? I assume he was made permanent;<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>he was still there in 1892 at the next kerfuffle when the Govt decided<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>abolish the Department, see 92-01-30.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>has acquitted himself to my satisfaction during the past six months. I would therefore respectfully recommend, that he be now permanently appointed. His Life-Insurance Policy for £100 (maximum) salary of present position £96) I beg to forward herewith.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your most obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Govt. Botanist</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The Under Secretary</p>
         </div>
